<postlude component="profesor"> 

  <!-- Posibles errores -->
  <paragraphs>
    <title><custom ref="errores-cool-titulo"/></title><p>[++++++++++++++++]</p>
    <p>Students explain that <m>\frac{4}{6}</m> is greater than <m>\frac{4}{3}</m> because 6 is greater than 3.</p>
  </paragraphs>


  <!-- Estrategia de apoyo si muchos estudiantes respondieron incorrectamente -->
  <paragraphs>
    <title><custom ref="apoyo-cool-titulo"/></title><p>[++++++++++++++++]</p>
    <p>During the launch of the next day's activity, have students pair up and discuss what the denominator of a fraction tells us and how it might help us compare two fractions.</p>
  </paragraphs>

</postlude>

</project>